DialogLines = Array[String](["Ah, a visitor! How magnifique. I have been unjustly imprisoned in this, how you say... flavorless dungeon.", "The crime, they say, is excessive butter usage. But what is 'excessive butter'? This is a philosophical question, non?", "When I escape I shall open a bakery. The first thing I shall bake is a cake filled with the finest... paperwork to clear my name."])

